description:
After Flawless's reality tearing fart opens a pathway to another dimension, multiple universes are thrown into absolute chaos. Join Flawless along with her reluctant magical moms, Trixie and Twilight Sparkle, as they dive snout first into this bizarre adventure filled with new and familiar faces! oco

On June 20th... Everything will change...
